{"tid":991352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"噁男電梯內熊抱小四女童　瘋狂搓胸30秒","createTime":"2019-01-22T10:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:32:16.000Z","uid":179810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcb817b7d11305f569412b0083419993269514a","tid":991352,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190113/640_95532ed07ad01982461823814d4507e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190113%2F640_95532ed07ad01982461823814d4507e9.jpg&h=031e7828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190113/640_9e28976fe3aebd845ba27b4ff7dece00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190113%2F640_9e28976fe3aebd845ba27b4ff7dece00.jpg&h=e857d99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n廣西南寧某社區日前傳出一段監視器影片，畫面震驚家長！一名小學四年級的女童在電梯中遭尾隨男子熊抱、搓胸，猥褻至少30秒。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國媒體報導，這起猥褻事件發生在上月21日晚上8時36分左右，女童當時拉著書包進入電梯，一名男子尾隨進入，當女童按下8樓按鍵後，男子也按了7樓。緊接著，男子先摸了女童的頭，然後將她一把摟進懷裡，從背後熊抱、搓胸，猥褻過程至少30秒；電梯到了7樓後，男子還將女童拉出去。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n當地媒體報導指出，女童曾向老師表示，她有跟家人反映自己「被人摸了一下」，但爸媽不以為意。事隔20天後，女童爸爸因為自己的汽車被人刮了，向社區調閱監視器畫面，連同電梯畫面一起取出，才驚覺女兒被人猥褻，女童媽媽憤而報警，現正調查中。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190113/1500047/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190113%2F1500047%2F&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b913c97a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190113%2F1500047%2F&h=9f54d9b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190113/1500047/</a><br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c131186fc580abbe498a1bfffaf4f5cbd694eb","tid":991352,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打"},{"pid":"341adb56345acd0a1cd1a58a2272b480b8e96403","tid":991352,"uid":15830,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"摸一下而已沒甚麼大不了的"},{"pid":"837993ee32ec51d230896e12fd8222691fdd067c","tid":991352,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"廣西咁多1樓1唔係冇原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但爸媽不以為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0442810e08f40c443d3bbaab3ce2228383ccdd43","tid":991352,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47975c4e6511361ce73c027989e1539d3d9be396","tid":991352,"uid":115042,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"架車花咗就要睇Cam,個女俾人抽水就唔出聲"},{"pid":"063477d8af00ef65c915b05e753651e710b322d2","tid":991352,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a945b108d017a9980c56ef0ba40d14e57c26ecab","tid":991352,"uid":172844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"原來摸一下就冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd576d49575bb229527005f345803db47b7f77e0","tid":991352,"uid":66547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:40:39.000Z","msg":"帶出電梯應該唔係摸左一下咁簡單"},{"pid":"812f6a2067a595bfceff24bd7c824b32fac25715","tid":991352,"uid":128741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10: